        About this item

        • Make it snow right in your own kitchen with the S900A Electric Shaved Ice Machine. Make a margarita, slushie, granita, iced coffee, or any other frozen snowball treat you can think of. Your own icy treat station at home. The Hawaiian Shaved Ice countertop snocone maker is simple to use and clean. Portable, easy to store when not in use.
        • Use cube ice, bagged ice, or make your own with the ice cups. Set includes Home-use electric S900A shaved ice and snow cone machine [3-piece design easy to assemble], 2 round block ice cups, a non-slip mat, and a 1-year manufacturers warranty. Powdery, chewable shaved ice. Prepare cool treats quickly at sleepovers, small pool parties, birthday parties, and other family and friend get-togethers.
        • Make 2 snowcones per ice block. High-quality, multifunctional machine comes with a 1-year manufacturers warranty. Give your blender a break and put a new twist on your evening cocktail, add flavor to your margarita, and other drinks, granitas, seltzers, Italian soda, icee, black coffee, hot chocolate, slushie, smoothies, shakes, popsicles, cola, and more.
        • Standard 120-volt electrical plug-in. The S900A electric shaved ice machine is easy to operate and stores conveniently away when not in use. Our syrups are best for food allergies. Shelf-stable high fructose corn syrup requires no refrigeration and is nut-free. None of the flavors contain soy, wheat, dairy, starch, flour, or egg products. Most syrups have a shelf life of 2 to 3 years. Not from concentrate, no need to add water.
        • Add a dash of flavor to nearly anything with our wide variety of syrup options. Not just for a shaved ice or snow cone machine! Check out our whole line of syrups, accessories, snowcone machines and cotton candy makers your own mini retro concession stand, right on your own kitchen counter. 5.5 wide, 8 diameter, and 12 tall which makes it easy to tuck under the counter or in a cabinet.

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        4.0 out of 5 stars Love this!
        Reviewed in the United States on June 28, 2023
        Verified Purchase
        Comes with 2 small ice containers to freeze water into discs. It shaves the ice perfectly just as if we had gone to a vendor selling shaved ice at the county fair. It is very easy to use just pop the ice disc out of the container, put it in the top of the machine, replace the top and press down on the large gray button. I would recommend using both hands when pressing down to keep constant pressure pushing down on the top of the machine to help keep it steady going. There 2 drawbacks: one being its noisy and may scare your pet (our cat runs out every time we use it and our dog barks because she knows she's getting an ice treat. Two, it does not use the entire disc of ice, leaving a thin disc about a quarter inch thick which is fine for us as we break the and use it in drinks or give the whole disc to the dog who loves chomping down on ice.. We usually mix tea, soda or juice for a nice slush drink if we want flavoring added. Most of the time, just eat the shaved ice plain. I would not recommend using ice cubes, it will wear out the blades, strain the motor, and will not produce the same shaved ice as what the discs provided will make.. Overall its a great product for at home shaved ice without all the sugary syrup added from commercial vendors.
